lyrics:
(spoken) Son, quit playin' in the dirt with yer pigs, and pick up yer banjo, poppa wants to sing a song!

[Verse]
weeelllllllll
That tracer from overwatch is one eye catcher
And i do gotta soft spot for widow makerrrrr
and i must say, i would find it titillating
[pause]
if they were to play soccer!

[Bridge]
Break it down, piggyboy!!!

[Chorus]
I want Overwatch soccer, I should be the referee,
They could play against League of Legends women maybe
And there could be post game interviews
Sponsored by Mountain Dew
Oh yes Overwatch soccer would be just fameux
The sport for me and you!
